{"tid":2186721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環保署：料稍後時間部分地區空氣質素達嚴重水平","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T12:20:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5aa59e5deeffb9c60db0b8931f427896d73392","tid":2186721,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"本港空氣質素持續欠佳。環保署預測稍後時間，部分一般及路邊空氣監測站的空氣質素健康指數可能達嚴重水平，預料在風力增強前，本港空氣污染仍會維持在較高水平。 <br />\n<br />\n環保署指，受強颱風美莎克及颱風海神的外圍環流影響，一股大陸氣流帶來高濃度背景污染，本港大致晴朗酷熱，吹微風，不利污染物擴散。<br />\n<br />\n署方表示，日間的陽光有利光化煙霧現象，令臭氧及微細懸浮粒子在珠江三角洲區域內迅速形成，巿區部分地區及路邊，較高的臭氧水平亦加速二氧化氮的形成。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2355544&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=dac4cc31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355544</a>"},{"pid":"13b4294da41368ab68b5560a246e58df6f63b511","tid":2186721,"uid":77196,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"支那世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"d4aef5a29f7e77fd92019f4fd34b86d9b8d91edc","tid":2186721,"uid":143499,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db58f1edc5213eaef484e3c5f79ae90ffe074b8a","tid":2186721,"uid":214502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"好彩有落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f1774e280fac5c1705ef8788c8ae0a3a826a97","tid":2186721,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">一股大陸氣流帶來高濃度背景污染</span></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中央送大禮, 等香港可以擋美國激光武器"},{"pid":"d644c7e2062d84feb6915d39fa1b2c